des:
"Mater Dei Radio is a Catholic broadcasting apostolate dedicated bringing souls to Jesus through the Blessed Virgin Mary.

Learn about our programs, podcasts, mobile app, and more at materdeiradio.com.

To LISTEN ON ALEXA:

Say, ""Alexa, play Mater Dei Radio!""
Our station is pronounced ""MAH - TARE DAY - EE,"" which is Latin for ""Mother of God.""

Questions? Please email info@materdeiradio.com.


DAILY BROADCAST HIGHLIGHTS:

Daily Mass: 5 am, 12 & 8 pm
Chaplet of Divine Mercy: 3 & 7 pm
The Rosary: 6:30 & 11:30 pm
The Morning Blend Live: 7 - 9 am (weekdays)
Catholic Answers Live: 3:30 - 5 pm (weekdays)
"
